@SysInclude { doc }
@SysInclude { svgmacros }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
Inline Mermaid passthrough -- the SVG back end should emit a
foreignObject wrapping a div.mermaid carrying the source. The
diagram itself only renders in a browser; rsvg-convert paints
the foreignObject as empty space, which is why this snippet is
classified graphics-heavy.
@LP
@Mermaid { "graph LR; A->B" }
@End @Text
